{"tid":1040234,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"其實Kepa係犧牲自己去拯救沙Sir","createTime":"2019-02-28T03:02:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-28T04:55:25.000Z","uid":33872,"like":8,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c793a02c1ee464d0e6fa71f6669f1601893e5207","tid":1040234,"uid":33872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T03:02:32.000Z","msg":"其實Kepa拒絕被換出完全係沙sir編寫既劇本<br />\n睇落沙sir俾後生仔恰覺得佢真係好慘好可憐<br />\n<br />\n但件事發生之後最大受益者就係沙sir自己<br />\n首先與論壓力令車仔高層唔敢企係班大帝球員個邊去炒沙sir<br />\n<br />\n第二可以成功係更衣室捉鬼 只要發現邊個企係kepa個邊個個就係鬼<br />\n<br />\n第三可以令其他人都因為可憐沙sir而轉為支持車仔 英國一號左閘查比亞就係一個好既例子<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以諒解Kepa 佢都係大局為重 用犧牲自己既名聲去拯救沙Sir 依種行為真係值得大家為佢喝采！"},{"pid":"9014ac2d3c5fda8fad073789b51920faac0885fe","tid":1040234,"uid":33872,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T04:02:01.000Z","msg":"一齊支持kepa"},{"pid":"da4ea392e2a9d8cbc41885998172ce67cfa2f1f0","tid":1040234,"uid":26959,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T04:16:14.000Z","msg":"請珍惜沙利"},{"pid":"7679a906bf82efa5ff8e3a8597fb2e190c25d459","tid":1040234,"uid":125070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T04:41:09.000Z","msg":"kepa好<br />\n好kepa<br />\n車狗出了一個好龍叫kepa<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fc4c35f24087ea7b468f68473919775afec754e","tid":1040234,"uid":30773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T04:53:14.000Z","msg":"兩個夾撚定"},{"pid":"94b71a2e529cdd650b88d3266ef578156fc9cc1f","tid":1040234,"uid":124458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T04:55:25.000Z","msg":"黑暗兵法 君子獻頭"}]}